                  </persName>
            , in the infirmary in the workhouse of the parish of St. Mary-le-bone, in the said County, in the presence and hearing of the prisoner, 
               <persName id="t18290115-195-person1567">
                  Benjamin 
                  Burrup
               <interp inst="t18290115-195-person1567" type="surname" value="Burrup"></interp>
